text: puok del chchek denhdaol nowknong ayeat robsa a l laoh daoy kmean phosdo tang namuoy ban mokadl puokke noh vea kuor aoy saabkhpaem da thom bamphot champoh a l laoh ning champoh banda anak del mean chomnue . dauchnaoh der a l laoh baohtra phchit towleu real chetd robsa anak del kraeutakratm phdachkar
